			"value": "<p><em>Ranged Weapon Attack:</em> [[/attack]], range 30/60 ft., one Large or smaller creature. <em>Hit:</em> The creature is restrained by webbing generated by the [[lookup @name lowercase]].</p><p><strong>Escape:</strong> As an action, the restrained creature can make a [[/check str]]{Strength check, DC 11}. On a success it escapes the webbing. The effect ends if the webbing is destroyed (AC 10, 5 hit points, vulnerable to fire, immune to bludgeoning).</p>",
